import React, { Component } from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import axios from 'axios' import { useParams } from "react-router-dom"; function withParams(Component) { return props => ; } class Example extends React.Component { constructor(props) { super(props); this.state = { count: 0 }; } async componentDidMount(){ const res = await axios.get('http://localhost:4000/chars') document.title = `You clicked ${this.state.val} times`; this.setState({ }) if(this.props.params.id){ const res = await axios.get('http://localhost:4000/chars' + this.props.params.id); this.setState({ _id: this.props.params.id, nombre: res.data.nombre, clase: res.data.clase, raza: res.data.raza, fuerza: res.data.fuerza, destreza: res.data.destreza, constitucion: res.data.constitucion, inteligencia: res.data.inteligencia, sabiduria: res.data.sabiduria, carisma: res.data.carisma }) } } render() { return (
